<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    {{!-- <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no"> --}}
    <title>{{data.fname}} {{data.lname}}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-DyZ88mC6Up2uqS4h/KRgHuoeGwBcD4Ng9SiP4dIRy0EXTlnuz47vAwmeGwVChigm" crossorigin="anonymous"/>


</head>

<body
    
    class="text-uppercase fw-bold d-xxl-flex justify-content-center align-items-center align-self-center mx-auto justify-content-xxl-center align-items-xxl-center"
    style="background: url(&quot;/assets/img/svg.png&quot;) bottom / cover space, #ffffff;height: 100vh;width: 100vw;">
    <div class="container-fluid pe-5 ps-5 ">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-9" ><img
                    src="/assets/img/image-removebg-preview%20(1).png" style="width: 400px;height: 95px;margin-top: 10px;"></div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div id="qrcode" style="float: right;" class="m-2"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 " >
                <p style="text-align: left; font-size: 15px;">
                    PASAPORTE <strong>/ PASSPORT</strong><br>{{data.passport}}<br><br>
                    Cédula<strong>/ ID</strong><br>{{data.personalID}}<br><br>
                    PACIENTE<strong> / PATIENT</strong><br>{{data.fname}} {{data.lname}} <br><br>
                    FECHA DE NACIMIENTO <strong>/ BIRTH DATE</strong><br>{{data.dob}}<br><br>
                    EDAD <strong>/ AGE</strong><br>{{data.age}}<br><br>
                    SEXO <strong>/ GENDER</strong><br>{{data.gender}}<br><br>
                    TELÉFONO <strong>/ PHONE</strong><br>{{data.phone}}<br><br>
                    DIRECCIÓN <strong>/ ADDRESS</strong><br>{{data.address}}<br>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 text-end"
                style="border-radius: 27px;border-style: dotted;padding: 13px;height: 247px;">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p style="margin-bottom: -19px;"><br>DESCRIPCIÓN DEL EXAMEN / EXAM
                            DESCRIPTION<br>SARS-CoV2<br>TIPO DE EXAMEN / SAMPLE TYPE<br>Hisopado Nasofaríngeo /
                            Nasopharyngeal Swab<br>PCR Molecular / Molecular PCR<br><br></p>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: -19px;">RESULTADO / RESULT</p><span
                            style="font-size: 45px;margin-top: 9px;" class="text-uppercase">
                               
                                {{#iseq data.testresult "Negativo"}} 
                                    <h1> <i class="fa fa-minus"> </i> NEGATIVO </h1>
                                {{/iseq}}

                                {{#iseq data.testresult "Positivo"}} 
                                      <h1 style="color: red"><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i> POSITIVO</h1>
                                {{/iseq}}
                                </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p style="text-align: right; font-size: 13px;"><br>DESCRIPCIÓN DEL EXAMEN / TEST DESCRIPTION<br>Se realizó detección de
                    SARS-CoV2, mediante amplificación isotérmica en termociclador para PCR en tiempo real, utilizando
                    indicadores específicos para la región conservada Nsp15 .que codifica una proteína no estructural
                    con actividad endoribonucleasa<br>&nbsp; Detection of SARS-CoV2, was performed by isothermal
                    amplification in a real-time PCR thermocycler, using specific primers for the conserved region
                    Nsp15, which encodes a non-structural protein with endoribonuclease activity<br></p>
                <p style="text-align: right;"><img src="/assets/img/image-removebg-preview.png"
                        style="width: 161px;height: 95px;"><br>Dr. Bad Bunny</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>



              <script type="text/javascript">
                var qrcode = new QRCode(document.getElementById("qrcode"), {
                  text: "{{data.url}}",
                  width: 128,
                  height: 128,
                  colorDark: "#000",
                  colorLight: "#ffffff",
                  correctLevel: QRCode.CorrectLevel.H
                });
              </script>
                  <script defer src="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/js/all.js" integrity="sha384-rOA1PnstxnOBLzCLMcre8ybwbTmemjzdNlILg8O7z1lUkLXozs4DHonlDtnE7fpc" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</body>

</html>